original_text: Record makers [UK health records] Plans for a massive cradle-to-grave electronic records project have been revealed by the government. Is the scheme really viable?
original_translation: El gobierno ha revelado planes para un proyecto masivo de registros electrónicos de cuna a tumba. ¿Es el plan realmente viable?
